{"tid":2117363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毋忘初心，毋忘憤怒，香港人緊記...（行動po）","createTime":"2020-07-20T20:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T01:39:03.000Z","uid":343629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12115342cae3ac82128daaf6b597ecc058989488","tid":2117363,"uid":343629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T20:25:07.000Z","msg":"請大家有意參與最少係721做其中一樣<br />\n表達自己追究7.21警黑合作毋忘抗爭<br />\n如果能夠做越多黎表態當然更好<br />\n希望一個行動盡自己最大承擔風險嘅能力做最多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCDv76D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCDv76D.png&h=4a9d6bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins>1.著黑衫</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins>2.帶長遮</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins>3.戴黑口罩</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins>4.戴抗爭飾物</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRbtUNX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRbtUNX.png&h=460ff1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><em><ins>《毋忘721恐襲，誓棄黨鐵》</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n行動：承諾7月21日罷搭黨鐵，身體力行將棄用八達通變成習慣大家要做啲セ：<br />\n1<strong><em>喺自己Facebook / IG / TG等出post承諾721當日罷搭黨鐵</em></strong><br />\n2<strong><em>喺Whatsapp / TG傳訊息嘅時候盡量落tag，例如＃721唔搭黨鐵＃今日唔用八仔＃你唱夠散紙未＃毋忘721，自創更佳</em></strong><br />\n3<strong><em>罷搭黨鐵@放棄使用八達通721集體退卡顯決心！回拒絕光顧黨鐵店舖及商場回「有心就唔怕煩黃色生活唔難」將退卡握返嘅錢捐俾有需要嘅手足/組織同撐黃店回邀請最少1位親友一齊參與</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFm5W2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFm5W2c.png&h=60643b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><em><ins>「勿忘洗手，健康步驟721」</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n免費派發視液樽旅行装疫情日趨嚴重，大家千祈一定要洗手，洗手，洗手！為了宣傳保持雙手衛生這個概念，酒店工會將連同香港調酒師工會，職工盟主席吳敏兒，元朗區麥業成議員，合作派發視液樽旅行装」，方便市民隨身攜帶消毒液，提醒大家「勿忘洗手，健康步驟721」，經常消毒！大家謹記每星期7日都要做足7個步驟洗手，每次洗手21秒。時時刻刻都要<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><em><ins>「勿忘721」</ins></em></strong></span></span>這個步驟。<br />\n日期：21/7星期二時間14：00-16：00<br />\n地點：元朗鳳攸北街休憩處（何已完握手位）<br />\n數量有限派完即止！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0TzQn2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0TzQn2.png&h=1d670c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><em><ins>名稱721一周年200萬人終極和你lunch</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n日期：7月21號星期（二）<br />\n時間：13：00<br />\n地點：中西區<br />\n活動目的：食lunch活動對象所有同路人留意事項<br />\n（重要）<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong><em><ins>帶身分證<br />\n自備文宣<br />\n近日活動受各方注意請各位手足在活動期間小心，避免再次發生暴力事件</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2ygjbG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2ygjbG.jpg&h=df9b08e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfZ3JDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfZ3JDn.png&h=591603ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03eWjbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03eWjbH.jpg&h=eb8746f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akFVzK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakFVzK2.jpg&h=98476686&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Asm9EbJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsm9EbJ.jpg&h=d9b71189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUS5cwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUS5cwJ.jpg&h=1b66c5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLoDxwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLoDxwK.jpg&h=6c7e7bca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dRYxwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dRYxwK.jpg&h=e63ad25d&s={SIZE}\"